OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FIndia makes cough syrup    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftesting mandatory for      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fexports                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Indian government has made it      
OL,6, compulsory for cough syrup makers to   
OL,7, get samples tested before exporting    
OL,8, their products.                        
OL,10,FStarting 1 June, these companies will  
OL,11,Fhave to get a certificate of analysis  
OL,12,Ffrom a government-approved laboratory. 
OL,14,FThe rule change comes after some       
OL,15,FIndian-made cough syrups were linked to
OL,16,Fdeaths in The Gambia and Uzbekistan.   
OL,18,FThe controversies had cast a pall over 
OL,19,FIndia's pharmaceutical industry, which 
OL,20,Fmakes a third of the world's medicines.
